OL,3,CBT fined #17.5 million for
OL,4,C'catastrophic failure' of 999 call
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FOfcom has fined BT #17.5 million after
OL,8,Fit failed to respond to a malfunction
OL,9,Fin its emergency call system that
OL,10,Flasted more than 10 hours.
OL,12,FThe regulator says BT suffered a
OL,13,Fnetwork disruption in June 2023
OL,14,Flasting ten-and-a-half hours affecting
OL,15,F14,000 emergency calls from more than
OL,16,F12,000 callers.
OL,18,FOfcom said the telecoms giant lacked
OL,19,F"sufficient warning systems", and that
OL,20,Fit did not have "adequate procedures"
OL,21,Fto assess and mitigate the outage.
