OL,3,CBT fined #17.5 million for
OL,4,C'catastrophic failure' of 999 call
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThe error led to handlers being logged
OL,8,Fout, calls being disconnected or
OL,9,Fdropped once transferred to the
OL,10,Femergency services, and calls being
OL,11,Freturned to the queue.
OL,13,FIt added that the disruption was found
OL,14,Fto be a configuration error in a file
OL,15,Fon BT's server, which caused call
OL,16,Fhandlers' systems to restart as they
OL,17,Freceived a call during the first hour
OL,18,Fof the crisis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
