OL,3,CBT fined #17.5 million for
OL,4,C'catastrophic failure' of 999 call
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FBT was unable to find the cause of the
OL,8,Fissue and attempted to switch to its
OL,9,Fdisaster recovery platform after
OL,10,Faround an hour.
OL,12,FThis procedure failed because of
OL,13,F"human error", as a result of
OL,14,F"instructions being poorly documented,
OL,15,Fand the team being unfamiliar with the
OL,16,Fprocess", Ofcom says.
