OL,3,CBT fined #17.5 million for
OL,4,C'catastrophic failure' of 999 call
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FThe company launched the disaster
OL,8,Frecovery platform successfully more
OL,9,Fthan two hours after the issue
OL,10,Fstarted, but the usual service was not
OL,11,Frestored as the platform "struggled
OL,12,Fwith demand".
OL,14,FThe issue lasted from 6:24AM to 4:56PM
OL,15,Fon June 25 last 2023.
