OL,3,CBT fined #17.5 million for
OL,4,C'catastrophic failure' of 999 call
OL,5,Csystem
OL,7,FSuzanne Carter, Ofcom's director of
OL,8,Fenforcement, said: "Being able to
OL,9,Fcontact the emergency services can
OL,10,Fmean the difference between life and
OL,11,Fdeath, so, in the event of any
OL,12,Fdisruption to their networks,
OL,13,Fproviders must be ready to respond
OL,14,Fquickly and effectively.
OL,16,F"In this case, BT fell woefully short
OL,17,Fof its responsibilities and was ill-
OL,18,Fprepared to deal with such a large-
OL,19,Fscale outage, putting its customers at
OL,20,Funacceptable risk."
